    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 49-15-21, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE PAYMENT OF MEMBERS OF THE DEPARTMENT OF MARINE RESOURCES ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS RESERVE UNIT FOR SPECIAL NEED EVENTS WITH CRITICAL SHORTAGES OF PERSONNEL; TO ESTABLISH CRITERIA FOR RESERVE OFFICERS TO BE ELIGIBLE TO BE PAID FOR SERVICE ON SPECIAL NEED EVENTS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
